{
  "texts": [
    "Beyond solving the technical issues of explainability methods as outlined above, there is also the need to adopt a holistic perspective towards XAI, such as making sure that development teams are diverse, integrating all involved stakeholders into the design process (see Sect.",
    "\"Multi-stakeholder participatory design\"), evaluating XAI methods in context (see Sect.",
    "\"The reproducibility crisis\"), etc.",
    "Further, it might be worth investigating XAI methods and values embedded into these systems from other perspectives, such as that of historically marginalized groups (see Sect.",
    "\"Intersectionality\")."
  ]
}